---
title: Chicken & Charred Corn Enchiladas with Tomato Salsa & Sour Cream
description: This easy dinner is guaranteed to put smiles on everyone’s dials. With tasty mouthfuls of Tex-Mex spiced chicken covered in rich enchilada sauce and gooey melted cheese, what’s not to like?
